data.Name: Qualcomm Incorporated
data.Description: Qualcomm Incorporated is a prominent American multinational corporation based in San Diego, California, renowned for its groundbreaking innovations in semiconductor and telecommunications technologies. As a leading force in mobile connectivity, Qualcomm specializes in developing cutting-edge solutions that drive global wireless communications, supported by a robust portfolio of essential patents related to 5G, 4G, and CDMA standards. Its strategic emphasis on advancing connectivity and computational capabilities across diverse industries positions Qualcomm as a pivotal player in the ongoing evolution of mobile technology and the Internet of Things (IoT), reinforcing its critical role within the technology landscape.
data.Address: 5775 MOREHOUSE DRIVE, SAN DIEGO, CA, UNITED STATES, 92121-1714
